<plot>Abigail's Reality is about the core of an emotional experience about a dying mother and a pregnant daughter. Covering over the course of two days, Abigail struggles confront her fears and pains about becoming a single mother and the haunting of her own pasts. Her mother, Isabel, has a dark secret so great that she does not want to concern her own daughter. Only Richard, Isabel's private doctor, knows the secret, realizes that the truth must be known and fills in the gap.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?021291</url></doc>
